{"tid":2040042,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有用既話幫我推兩野","createTime":"2020-05-28T10:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T12:54:29.000Z","uid":24930,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"40155a74381aa190949faa4b236d044e261c0f34","tid":2040042,"uid":24930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:25:51.000Z","msg":"其實根本就唔係唔想出<br />\n就算你話CCP vs USA都好<br />\n行出街頭都有佢既丁點意義係到<br />\n<br />\n見到班仆街叫手足歸位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實手足不知幾撚想歸位<br />\n但點解出唔到？唔敢出？<br />\n因為出去成本太撚高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人愈少 冇掩護 根本去到目的地都成問題<br />\n仲未計換裝呢？ 真係做野呢？<br />\n之前點解大部分手足可以全身而退？<br />\n因為人夠多 服裝一致呀<br />\n我求其搵個冇cam位換完full black block返大隊<br />\n你睇一世都搵唔到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以點解要開呢個post<br />\n唔係要鳩叫人出/唔出<br />\n要為以後街頭抗爭做好準備<br />\n請從今開始 叫埋你身邊既人<br />\n一齊著一致既服裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ne.g. 基本既full blackblock, 全白, 我❤️警察藍<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">每日/每週服裝統一由各大平台發佈</span></span><br />\n咁先可以真正掩護到手足出黎<br />\n記住作左和理非既你 有好多野可以幫到真正做事既人<br />\n即使拉左你 48個鐘之後都係一條好漢<br />\n身上冇任何野 冇做任何野既你 就算比人charge都唔撚會告得你入 統一服裝既存在 已經係對手足極大既幫助<br />\n唔想見到大家陷入左個循環 下次再call又出唔到黎<br />\n出到黎都冇哂文具<br />\n要禁？禁止香港人著衫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然幾丁友係成唔到事<br />\n覺得呢個建議有用既話 幫我share下推多幾野<br />\n純粹初步諗法<br />\n有更好既諗法不妨講埋出黎討論下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c63d0ce9017b4e7bd5573e7d102318232add818","tid":2040042,"uid":24930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"e77955e060541f4dc82f28f9f554c16bdb3167b2","tid":2040042,"uid":24930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"435d513a69e7091c28ac23f806722437e2a290ea","tid":2040042,"uid":24930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"如果真係有成效 我唔介意毒撚推到2046<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7049c1d0ff9c54df643313f1f0a121369415e553","tid":2040042,"uid":24930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:32:07.000Z","msg":"睇完幫我推兩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb89973d44485d9124c4c5c5e3696ddf72358db","tid":2040042,"uid":141700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"每次唔同色衫都幾好 起碼藍絲唔識分 少左啲報串撚"},{"pid":"cb82fe66ac9787e257f35d1a8cc279f1745cf996","tid":2040042,"uid":24930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係正評 推一推ok? 開左政事台係咪冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676ca88d9527202c181a43b86790eafb7fb4abae","tid":2040042,"uid":24930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddb89973d44485d9124c4c5c5e3696ddf72358db","tid":2040042,"uid":141700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"每次唔同色衫都幾好 起碼藍絲唔識分 少左啲報串撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"間唔中又轉下 就算你知我今日咩色都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話唔定你已經著左出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4c7587e8295348ad0b0e4c1e2114b905f43efd","tid":2040042,"uid":60733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n不過講緊唔告先係48<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\